  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study the prevalence of delirium among old persons with home-nursing care living in the
      community. By recruiting the persons in a stable phase, the investigators wish to study the
      influence of an episode of delirium upon further cognitive and physical function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
